high_descs: Turn left to walk into the living room to face the couch.
Pick up the potato on the right from the couch.
Turn right and walk up to the microwave in the kitchen.
Heat the potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to reach the fridge on the left.
Put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the hot potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and enter the next room and go near the couch
Pick up the potato from the couch
Turn left and go to the counter
Turn left and go near the oven and bake the potato
anns.task_desc: Bake the potato lying on the couch

high_descs: Leave the bedroom, take a left and go to the first couch in the living room.
Pick up the potato on the right side of the couch.
Go into the kitchen and open the microwave door.
Put the potato in the microwave, cook it, then take it out.
Turn around and open the refrigerator door and put the potato in the refrigerator.
Close the door on the refrigerator.
